First Department,

September, 1983

(September 15, 1983) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Waldo Grant, Appellant.

— Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County (Peter J. McQuillan, J.), rendered on May 23, 1978, unanimously affirmed. Application by appellant’s counsel to withdraw as counsel is granted. (See Anders v California, 386 US 738; People v Saunders, 52 AD2d 833.) We have reviewed this record and agree with appellant’s assigned counsel that there are no meritorious points which could be raised on this appeal. Concur — Kupferman, J. P., Sullivan, Ross, Milonas and Alexander, JJ.
